title: The Risk of Stepping Out On Your Own with @hairbymarissasue
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew sat down with @hairbymarissasue to talk about balancing motherhood with being a business owner, working behind the chair, hiring assistants and how scary/rewarding it can be to branch out on your own. This is an episode you won't want to miss!
